  "title": "Enrolled Nurse",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Enrolled Nurse</strong></u></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support Registered Nurses (RNs) in the coordination of care of patients</li>\n  <li>Assist  physicians and RNs in bedside procedures and treatment</li>\n  <li>Communicate effectively and maintain collaborative relationship with the multidisciplinary healthcare team members</li>\n  <li>Provide patient education to patients, Next of Kin (NOK) and caregivers on self-care management</li>\n  <li>Attend to and assist RNs in patient resuscitation or medical emergencies</li>\n  <li>Support clinical supervision of new enrolled nurses, support care staff and coaching of nursing students in the delivery of nursing care</li>\n  <li>Identify common causes of patient safety incidents and work with the supervisor and senior nurses in carrying out quality improvement activities</li>\n  <li>Be a team player and participate in clinical audits as required</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate must be enrolled with SNB</li>\n  <li>NITEC  in Nursing or State Enrolled Nurse Certificate</li>\n  <li>At least 1 year of experience as Enrolled Nurse in relevant discipline</li>\n</ul>",
